          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-1" n="1">Here <hi rend="red-ink">Sarum</hi> lies, of late so wise,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-2" n="2">As learned as <hi rend="red-ink">Aquinas</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-3" n="3">Lawn Sleeves, he wore, yet was no more</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-4" n="4">a Christian than <hi rend="red-ink">Socinus</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-5" n="5">oaths Pro and Con he swallowed down</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-6" n="6">Loved God like any Lay Man,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-7" n="7">Wrote, Preached and prayed, but yet betrayed</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-8" n="8">Gods Holy Church for Mammon</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-9" n="9">Of every vice He had a spice,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-10" n="10">although a Reverend Prelate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-11" n="11">Yet lived and died, if not belied</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-12" n="12">a true dissenting zealot.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-13" n="13">If such a Soul to Heaven should strole</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-14" n="14">And scape old <hi rend="red-ink-large">Satans</hi> clutches,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-15" n="15">We may presume there is full room</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-766O-line-16" n="16">For <hi rend="red-ink-large">Marlbrough</hi> and his <hi rend="red-ink-large">Dutchess</hi>.</l>
          </lg>
